# External Feeds & APIs: Images

- Extract image URLs from external content (e.g. first image in description/CDATA or API `image`/`thumbnail`)
- Add optional `image?: string` to parsed/typed items and component props
- When `image` is present, render with `loading="lazy"`, descriptive `alt`, and optional link to source
- CSP: ensure `img-src` allows the image domain (e.g. `https:` or specific host)
- Next.js: add remote host to `images.remotePatterns` in config, or use plain `<img>` for third-party images
